1. Change the background color for the webpage to a gradient

2. Create a heading and add any type of animation to it


ANSWERS:

HTML:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
    	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="FILE_PATH_NAME.css">
    </head>
    <body>
    	<div class = "text">
        	<h1 id = "title">Hello World</h1>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>

CSS: 


html{
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #00BFFF, #E0FFFF);
}
#title{
	font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadein 2s;
    animation-delay: 1.5s;
}

@keyframes fadein {
  0% {
    opacity: 0.0;
  }
  100% {
    opacity: 1.0;
  }
}
